reviewText: The grandkids loved it. It had there last name in the title!
This is one of my daughter's favorite DVDs. She has loved Kaput and Zosky since they were on NickToons, so we got this as one of her birthday gifts last year.
I would rate this product 5 stars because this was a gift for a 7 year old who is in love with the show and would rate it a 10 if she could, so I am for her.
